OL,3,CJury in Jeffrey Donaldson trial begin
OL,4,Cthird day of deliberations
OL,6,FThe jury in the sex offences trial of
OL,7,Fformer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson has resumed deliberations at
OL,9,FNewry Crown Court.
OL,11,FThe jury of seven men and five women
OL,12,Fhas already considered its verdicts
OL,13,Ffor seven hours over two days.
OL,15,FThe 63-year-old former MP has pleaded
OL,16,Fnot guilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
