OL,3,CJury in Jeffrey Donaldson trial begin
OL,4,Cthird day of deliberations
OL,6,FHis wife, Eleanor Donaldson, 60,
OL,7,Fdenies several charges of aiding and
OL,8,Fabetting her husband's alleged
OL,9,Foffending.
OL,11,FShe is facing a trial of the facts on
OL,12,Fmental health grounds.
OL,14,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,15,Fevidence in the case but cannot result
OL,16,Fin a criminal conviction.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
